{"commands": [{"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "\n%md-sandbox\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 0; padding-top: 9px;\">\n  <img src=\"https://databricks.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/db-academy-rgb-1200px.png\" alt=\"Databricks Learning\" style=\"width: 1200px\">\n</div>", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "a7146865-8e33-4fbf-a867-aa7171686097", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "880fc332-6f0d-44bf-b726-38b23b30e14c", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 1, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md-sandbox\n<img src=\"https://files.training.databricks.com/images/Apache-Spark-Logo_TM_200px.png\" style=\"float: left: margin: 20px\"/>\n\nRead the Stock Orders bronze Delta table. Deduplicate and write the resulting DataFrame to the silver Delta table after executing a few datetime transformations.\n\n# Bronze To Silver - Stock Transactions\n\n## In this exercise you will:\n* Learn how to deduplicate your data using performant Spark API\n* Practice windowing and specifying windows\n* Practice using ranking over windows for deduplication \n* Practice handling and transforming datetime fields with built-in functions like `year`, `month` and others\n\n## Prerequisites\n* Web browser: **Chrome**\n* A cluster configured with **8 cores** and **DBR 7.0**", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "627e3e05-4f95-48d4-ad94-0ca63b346800", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "04876da9-765c-4f30-b940-8e7b9fdb66bd", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 2, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md-sandbox\n<h2 style=\"color:red\">Instructor Note</h2>\n\n\n\nThings to talk about:\n- talk about the goal:\n  - what are we building right now: deduplicated claims table with fixed timestamp columns\n  - why is it useful: resolving duplication errors by selecting desired output value (in this case: oldest entry)\n- describe how Spark Windows works and how to use rank function with them for deduplication", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "70c21506-0a47-45c9-b099-cbee71f87e47", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "7df8b35a-907c-4c79-9aa8-c103c56ae1c6", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 3, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n## ![Spark Logo Tiny](https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png) Classroom-Setup<br>\n\nFor each lesson to execute correctly, please make sure to run the **`Classroom-Setup`** cell at the start of each lesson (see the next cell) and the **`Classroom-Cleanup`** cell at the end of each lesson.", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "19900076-b738-4a51-8509-acade8347527", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "f89f7fa4-3272-460e-99c7-e230175f2c74", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 4, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%run ./Includes/PCF-11S-ClassroomSetup", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "0765c240-c74e-49df-aa0b-b7b07b48d9d6", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "44efc975-790c-4f73-a9f4-7d99e333ee8a", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 5, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n## ![Spark Logo Tiny](https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png) Steps to complete<br>\nImplement the **`challenge()`** function to achieve the following:\n\n- Read the Stock Orders table from **`bronzeStockOrdersPath`** into a DataFrame.\n- Drop duplicates: some stock orders (**`transaction_id`**) have been duplicated - for each **`transaction_id`**, keep the oldest one by using **`ordertime`** (hint: use window and rank functions). Assign the result to a new variable name and do the transformations described below.\n- Currently **`ordertime`** is in unixtime format. Create a new column named **`order_timestamp`** from the **`ordertime`** column by converting it to timestamp.\n- There are useful built-in functions in Spark. Here we can use some of them:\n- Create a new column named **`year`** from the **`order_timestamp`** column, which shows the year.\n- Create a new column named **`month`** from the **`order_timestamp`** column, which shows the month.\n- Create a new column named **`day`** from the **`order_timestamp`** column, which shows the day.\n- Create a new column named **`dow`** from the **`order_timestamp`** column, which shows the day of the week.\n- Write the resulting DataFrame to **`targetDirectory`** as a Delta table using the overwrite mode.\n\n**`bronzeStockOrdersPath`** and **`targetDirectory`** have already been defined in your environment.\n\nThe resulting DataFrame schema should look like this:\n\n|name|type|\n|---|---|\n|clicked_items|ArrayType(ArrayType(StringType,true),true)|\n|investor|LongType|\n|ordertime|LongType|\n|price|DoubleType|\n|ticker|StringType|\n|transaction_id|LongType|\n|type|StringType|\n|volume|LongType|\n|order_timestamp|TimestampType|\n|year|IntegerType|\n|month|IntegerType|\n|day|IntegerType|\n|dow|IntegerType|", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "3309c420-4f9e-4e3e-a6ea-6cc1d558c1a4", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "694d6cda-d54c-45dc-a678-d248b5064f0e", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 6, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "// ANSWER\n\ndef solution(spark:org.apache.spark.sql.SparkSession, bronzeStockOrdersPath:String, targetDirectory:String) : DataFrame = {\n  import org.apache.spark.sql.expressions.Window\n  import org.apache.spark.sql.functions._\n  \n  // Read the Stock Orders bronze table from the `bronzeStockOrdersPath` and assign it to a variable `stockOrders`\n  val stockOrders = spark.read.format(\"delta\").load(bronzeStockOrdersPath)\n  \n  // `transaction_id` column in `stockOrders` has duplicates - keep the oldest one by `ordertime` (hint:Windowing), assign it to a new variable name\n  val res = stockOrders\n  val res2 = res.withColumn(\n       \"rank\", rank().over(Window.partitionBy(\"transaction_id\").orderBy(col(\"ordertime\")))\n                    ).filter(col(\"rank\") === 1).drop(\"rank\")\n  \n  // Create a new column named `order_timestamp` from the `ordertime` column by converting it to timestamp.\n  // Extract the year from `order_timestamp` into the `year` column.\n  // Extract the month from `datetime` into the `month` column.\n  // Extract the day of month from `datetime` into the `day` column.\n  // Extract the day of week from `datetime` into the `dow` column.\n  val res3 = (res2.withColumn(\"order_timestamp\", from_unixtime(col(\"ordertime\")).cast(\"timestamp\"))\n            .withColumn(\"year\", year(col(\"order_timestamp\")))\n            .withColumn(\"month\", month(col(\"order_timestamp\")))\n            .withColumn(\"day\", dayofmonth(col(\"order_timestamp\")))\n            .withColumn(\"dow\", dayofweek(col(\"order_timestamp\")))\n             )\n  \n  // Write the resulting DataFrame to `targetDirectory` as a Delta table using the overwrite mode and overwrite schema option.\n  res3.write.mode(\"overwrite\").format(\"delta\").option(\"overwriteSchema\", \"true\").save(targetDirectory)  \n\n  // Return the resulting DataFrame:\n  return res3\n}\nval finalDF = solution(spark, bronzeStockOrdersPath, targetDirectory)\ndisplay(finalDF)", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "f69596d3-fd06-4861-8f92-39d505e91292", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "58954dcc-bd18-4a65-9020-bb0f4391f0ee", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 7, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n<h2><img src=\"https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png\"> Reality Check</h2>\n\nRun the following cell to make sure you are on track:", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "3f07b13d-1c92-46bc-a43a-d7789bcc6dea", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "8f747354-a3ce-4462-b46a-872de5e08a97", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 8, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "// ANSWER - Test your solution\nrealityCheck(solution, spark, bronzeStockOrdersPath, targetDirectory)", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "46ad5244-6651-49ba-99e8-9b6ca7c594e4", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "b287b6f5-d0d0-47cd-a684-e96e4bbb3329", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 9, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n## ![Spark Logo Tiny](https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png) Classroom-Cleanup<br>\n\nRun the **`Classroom-Cleanup`** cell below to remove any artifacts created by this lesson.", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "4592d259-191d-4675-98e6-9ee0e66c69f4", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "57db425e-3680-476f-8907-e5af5ae10305", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 10, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%run ./Includes/Classroom-Cleanup", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "4b14d75d-b834-4a2c-8f12-58fc3fde2f93", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false